Drawings prepared from the holotype of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rodda &amp; Simonsson" authorityYear="2011" box="[739,935,1941,1964]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Apocynaceae" genus="Hoya" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="1" pageNumber="38" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rotundiflora">
